                   net.nemein.reservations Changelog
                   ---------------------------------
Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guaranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completly new features.

2007-05-31 adrenalin
  - Multiple calendar views are now maintained after changing the month in calendar view

2007-04-12 adrenalin
  - Fixed Midgard 1.7 failure on fetching resources by GUID when showing multiple
    resources

2007-04-11 adrenalin
  + Added support for repeating events

2007-04-02 adrenalin
  + Added support for selecting multiple calendars for comparing

2007-03-22 rambo
  + reservations (per day) list view
  - heuristics for setting the *event* location
  - localizations

2007-03-20 rambo
  + support for separate privilege for reserving resources
  + support for anonymous reserving of resources
  - link root event privilege editor to toolbar

2007-01-09 bergie
  + Enabled editing and deleting of reservations

2007-01-08 bergie
  + Minor style improvements

2007-01-05 bergie
  + Initial working version of the new reservations system

2006-12-08 bergie
  ! Started refactoring for MidCOM 2.6+ technology

2006-06-29 rambo
  - made workable in 1.6 midgard as well (dont ask)
  - onsite reservation details and print views
  - 5min grace period to "start in past" check
  - display past reservations for 2h
  - edit/delete buttons for visible reservations to NAP toolbar (TODO: check how to notify NAP cache about this)

2005-09-15 torben
  - Fixed error reporting during reservation cycle.

2005-10-07 bergie
  + Made date inputs use JScalendar
  + Added sensible defaults to start and end dates
  + More WAI compatibility
  + Skipped "sudo" if user already has ownership of root event
  + Implemented hCalendar for reservation listings

2005-02-11 torben
  - Adapted to the new Metadata system.

2004-11-30 torben
  - NAP/AIS toolbar upgrade
  - Minor code cleanup

2004-11-10 torben
  - Filesystem conversion
  - Fixed incomplete default configuration

2004-08-25 torben
  - First working version

2004-07-13 torben
  - Initial Checkin
